---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import portlandMap from "../images/home/portland-map.webp";
import seattleMap from "../images/home/seattle-map.webp";
---

<section class="mb-14 flex flex-col justify-evenly bg-gray-200 bg-opacity-70 py-8">
  <div class="m-auto w-full max-w-4xl p-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold drop-shadow-sm">Catch us in your city! ğŸŒ</h1>
    <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-extrabold drop-shadow-sm">Currently in:</h2>
    <div class="mb-8 flex justify-evenly">
      <a href="/" class="relative bottom-0 flex w-48 flex-col items-center rounded-md border-4 border-gray-900 shadow-test transition-all duration-150 hover:bottom-2">
        <Image src={seattleMap} alt="Seattle Map" />
        <p class="p-3 text-lg">Seattle, WA</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="relative bottom-0 flex w-48 flex-col items-center rounded-md border-4 border-gray-900 shadow-test transition-all duration-150 hover:bottom-2">
        <Image src={portlandMap} alt="Portland Map" />
        <p class="p-3 text-lg">Portland, OR</p>
      </a>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">+ Are you looking to connect with some amazing bgirls in your city?</h2>
    <p class="mb-8 text-lg">
      Just send us a message on Instagram and we'll do our best to connect you with talented dancers in your area. Even if we don't have a Cypher Queenz crew established in your city yet, we'll still do our best to make some introductions for you.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">+ Want to stay up to date on all things Cypher Queenz?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg">
      Be sure to add your name to our mailing list for newsletters and future updates. Don't miss out - <a href="/mailing-list" style="font-variant:small-caps;" class="text-3xl font-extrabold">sign up now!</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
